description: Join us to make natural soap from Vietnamese Herbs. In the soap making session, we will use Vietnam's specialties such as coffee, cajeput oil and gac oil. The demonstration will take place in 54 Quan Su street, house of late musician Do Xuan Oanh, composer of Vietnam's hictoric song "August Nineteenth". The song marks the first day of August Revolution, which ended with Vietnam's National Day.
